::Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike shruggs at Skulletron's question. He looks down at his wrist, 
activating his comm-link. "Zardus, are you busy."

"At the moment, yes," Zardus' voice replies, "There is a new soldier that 
requires reprogramming."

Bloodystrike looks back at Skulletron. "He's busy right now. Reprogramming a 
new soldier."
